interface.name: Cloud SQL Proxy
interface.summary: allows user to connect to Cloud SQL without IP whitelisting or SSL certificates
interface.description: The Cloud SQL Proxy allows a user with the appropriate permissions to connect to a Second Generation Cloud SQL database without having to deal with IP whitelisting or SSL certificates manually.

interface.name: Drupal-SMTP
interface.description: This module allows Drupal to bypass the PHP mail() function and send email directly to an SMTP server. The module supports SMTP authentication and can even connect to servers using SSL if supported by PHP.

interface.name: OpenTTD
interface.summary: Open Source clone of Transport Tycoon Deluxe
interface.description: OpenTTD is an open source clone of the Microprose game "Transport Tycoon Deluxe", a popular game originally written by Chris Sawyer. It attempts to mimic the original game as closely as possible while extending it with new features.

interface.description: E is a scripting language designed for writing secure distributed programs. This package adds support for using it with the SWT widget set.
